These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, emerald, azure, yellow
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, journalist, musician, firefighter
City: liverpool, boston, san-francisco, edinburgh
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, ship, train, tram
 1. the doctor is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 3. the person who likes pink is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the journalist##1
 5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
 6. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
 7. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
 9. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the musician##3
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person who likes pink##7
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
12. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
13. the person driving the tram is the person traveling to edinburgh##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color   | yellow    | emerald | azure    | pink   |
| Job   | doctor | musician | journalist | firefighter |
| City           | boston       | san-francisco   | edinburgh  | liverpool     |
| Transport     | bike      | train   | tram    | ship    |

