.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, mouse, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, skateboard, train
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indonesian, italian
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, doctor, fisherman, teacher
 1. the teacher is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
 2. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
 3. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
 4. the fisherman is the australian##1
 5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 6. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
 7. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the doctor and the australian##7
 8. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
10. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
11. the chinese is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | rabbit   | mouse       | ferret    | hedgehog      |
| Transport   | van | train | airplane         | skateboard   |
| Nationality   | italian   | australian  | chinese       | indonesian |
| Job         | librarian      | fisherman  | teacher | doctor |

