4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, cain, swisher, fonseca
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, train, snowmobile, motorbike
 1. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the fan of metal and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 3. the fan of reggae is the cain-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
 5. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
 6. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 7. the fan of rock is not the person watching crime movies##6
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the fan of salsa##6
 9. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person watching crime movies##3
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the fan of reggae is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
12. the swisher-smoker is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
| Music-Genre           | salsa | metal | reggae | rock |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | zombie    | crime    | martial-arts    |
