 2. the davidoff-smoker is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
 4. the person who's sport is surfing is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person traveling to boston##6
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 8. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is the person traveling to boston##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
11. the swisher-smoker is not the person traveling to boston##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |        3        |      4       |
