 4. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the taxi##7
 8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the person driving the helicopter##6
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
10. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
11. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Hobby         | chess      | cooking   | sudoku   | puzzles       |
| Color   | purple | azure    | orange | emerald       |
| City   | hannover  | san-francisco | prague   | rome     |
| Transport         | helicopter   | skateboard    | taxi   | quad-bike |

