.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, turkish, indian, american
4 different games are played: whist, billiard, bridge, domino
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, journalist, social-worker, scientist
4 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, hamster, rabbit
 1. the scientist is on the left of the indian##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
 3. the scientist is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the hamster##2
 4. the dressmaker is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 5. the person playing billiard is not the owner of the goldfish##6
 6. the scientist is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 7. the american is somewhere between the thai and the person playing domino##7
 8. the american is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 9. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the scientist##1
11. the thai is the person playing bridge##1
12. the person playing bridge is not the owner of the hamster##6

.:: Answer ::.
