The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bus, helicopter, quad-bike
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, indie, rock
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
 2. the fan of electronic is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person driving the airplane##2
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of funk is not the person driving the helicopter##6
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in april##7
 8. the fan of electronic is not the person who's birthday is in april##6
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
10. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
11. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the fan of rock##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person who's sport is surfing##6
13. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
14. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
15. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3

