.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, monopoly, canasta
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, daisy, tulip
House: craftsman, farmhouse, victorian, gothic-revival
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the gothic-revival house##1
 4. the victorian house is between the person playing canasta and the person playing scrabble##2
 5. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5
 6. the craftsman house is somewhere between the person who growsdaisy and the person playing snooker##7
 7. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person who growsmarigold##5
 8. the craftsman house is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
10. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game   | canasta      | monopoly     | scrabble   | snooker    |
| Flower     | tulip | daisy   | marigold | poppy |
| House     | gothic-revival        | victorian     | craftsman  | farmhouse      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 